a>，0-10岁</div><div id='95215cc59fed400c9527879f29db8747' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1032&endYear=1032')\">1032年</a>，生于黄陂县。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1033&endYear=1033')\">1033年</a>，随父居黄陂。弟程颐出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1034&endYear=1040')\">1034-1040年</a>，随父居黄陂。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1041&endYear=1041')\">1041年</a>，在黄陂，赋《酌贪泉》诗，曰：“中心如自固，外物岂能迁？”当世先达许其志操。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1042&endYear=1042')\">1042年</a>，随父居黄陂？<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.015388,"Longitude":119.613436,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN321181","Title":"丹阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4e6f1c94de9647aa9f828e8c166dc1a5\");'><span id='4e6f1c94de9647aa9f828e8c166dc1a5_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1043&endYear=1045')\">1043-1045年</a>，11-13岁</div><div id='4e6f1c94de9647aa9f828e8c166dc1a5' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1043&endYear=1043')\">1043年</a>，居丹阳庠序中，如老成人，户部侍郎彭思永至学舍，一见异之，许妻以女。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1044&endYear=1045')\">1044-1045年</a>，随父居润州？<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":25.407817,"Longitude":114.368357,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN360723","Title":"大余","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"44681968d63246f6916c0cbee115edcf\");'><span id='44681968d63246f6916c0cbee115edcf_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1051')\">1046-1051年</a>，14-19岁</div><div id='44681968d63246f6916c0cbee115edcf' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1046&endYear=1046')\">1046年</a>，随父居南安。师事周敦颐。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1047&endYear=1050')\">1047-1050年</a>，随父居南安。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1051&endYear=1051')\">1051年</a>，随父居南安？<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":32.064735,"Longitude":118.802891,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN3201","Title":"南京","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"0cc246895b6e41bf8d0e0a8654549364\");'><span id='0cc246895b6e41bf8d0e0a8654549364_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1052&endYear=1053')\">1052-1053年</a>，20-21岁</div><div id='0cc246895b6e41bf8d0e0a8654549364' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1052&endYear=1053')\">1052-1053年</a>，随父居江宁？母亲侯夫人卒。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"7ff03ddb1b02449d80880ef63fec88eb\");'><span id='7ff03ddb1b02449d80880ef63fec88eb_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1064')\">1061-1064年</a>，29-32岁</div><div id='7ff03ddb1b02449d80880ef63fec88eb' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1061')\">1061年</a>，任上元主簿。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1061&endYear=1061')\">1061年9月1日</a>，在上元，女儿出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1062&endYear=1062')\">1062年</a>，摄上元县令，为政有方。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1063&endYear=1063')\">1063年</a>，摄上元县令。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年8月4日</a>，在上元，子端悫出生。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.918137,"Longitude":106.52856,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN610330","Title":"凤县","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5e6f8334b0934b6480be129429a76b75\");'><span id='5e6f8334b0934b6480be129429a76b75_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1055')\">1055年</a>，23岁</div><div id='5e6f8334b0934b6480be129429a76b75' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1055&endYear=1055')\">1055年</a>，随父居凤州。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.802941,"Longitude":114.313904,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4102","Title":"开封","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"198434f8ab234be1a512abc193d41131\");'><span id='198434f8ab234be1a512abc193d41131_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1056&endYear=1057')\">1056-1057年</a>，24-25岁</div><div id='198434f8ab234be1a512abc193d41131' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1056&endYear=1056')\">1056年</a>，到汴京应试。卜葬祖考于伊川，遂居河南。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1057&endYear=1057')\">1057年</a>，登进士第。<span class='label'>作品：</span>南庙试佚道使民赋。南庙试九叙惟歌论。南庙试策五道。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"379494729d294f4ba71282f4ce0dc1d2\");'><span id='379494729d294f4ba71282f4ce0dc1d2_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1070')\">1068-1070年</a>，36-38岁</div><div id='379494729d294f4ba71282f4ce0dc1d2' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1068&endYear=1068')\">1068年5月14日</a>，在汴京，子端悫夭折。<span class='label'>作品：</span>程邵公墓志。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年4月</a>，在汴京任农田水利使。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年8月</a>，在汴京，以吕公著荐授太子中允权监察御史里行。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，在汴京任监察御史里行。<span class='label'>作品：</span>论王霸劄子。论君道疏。<span class='inlineComment2'>（论君道疏，即《二程集》中“上殿劄子”）</span>请修学校尊师儒取士劄子。论十事劄子。论养贤劄子。乞留张载状。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1069&endYear=1069')\">1069年</a>，在汴京任监察御史里行，与王安石论事不合；王安石称程颢之学“如上壁言难行也”，程颢说安石之学“如捉风”。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年3月4日</a>，在汴京任监察御史里行，与孙觉、吕公著、张戬、李常极论新法不便。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年</a>，在汴京任监察御史里行，上疏论新法不便。<span class='label'>作品：</span>谏新法疏。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年</a>，在汴京任监察御史里行，再上疏论新法不便。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年</a>，在汴京任监察御史里行，赴中堂议事，王安石方怒言者，厉色待之，程颢曰：“天下之事，非一家私议，愿公平气以听。”王为之愧屈。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年4月19日</a>，在汴京，辞京西路提点刑狱。<span class='label'>作品：</span>辞京西提刑奏状。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"b329e9ab78ef4eb78de77ec066753e31\");'><span id='b329e9ab78ef4eb78de77ec066753e31_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，45岁</div><div id='b329e9ab78ef4eb78de77ec066753e31' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年5月1日</a>，因贾昌衡、李南公推荐，改太常寺丞。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，汴京为官。与王尚恭诗歌唱和，作《和王安之五首》<span class='label'>作品：</span>小园。野轩。污亭。药轩。晚晖亭。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">晚晖亭（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->亭下花光春正好，亭头山色晚尤佳。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->欲知剩占清<span class=\"small\">①</span>风处，思顺街东第一家。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 原校：一作春</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年7月5日</a>，汴京为官。邵雍卒。<span class='label'>作品：</span>邵尧夫先生墓志铭。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4e36e50826b947f9a21955e7441e7e39\");'><span id='4e36e50826b947f9a21955e7441e7e39_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，45岁</div><div id='4e36e50826b947f9a21955e7441e7e39' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年冬</a>，张载辞官归，过洛与程颢、程颐议论；二程推赏《西铭》（即《订顽》）<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年12月乙亥？</a>，张载卒于临潼馆舍。<span class='label'>作品：</span>哭张子厚先生。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">哭张子厚先生（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押尤韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->叹息斯文约共修，如何夫子便长休。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->山东<span class=\"small\">①</span>无复苍生望，西土谁共后学求。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->千古声名联棣萼，二年零落去山丘。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->寝门恸哭知何限，岂独交亲念旧游<span class=\"small\">②</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 涂本作东山　② 以上《二程全书·二程文集》卷一</span></div></div>\r\n<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.114791,"Longitude":108.61136,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN610125","Title":"户县","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e295099c0b4042e6afe082e86850434a\");'><span id='e295099c0b4042e6afe082e86850434a_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1060')\">1058-1060年</a>，26-28岁</div><div id='e295099c0b4042e6afe082e86850434a' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1058&endYear=1058')\">1058年</a>，任鄠县主簿。<span class='label'>作品：</span>答横渠张子厚先生书。<span class='inlineComment2'>（答横渠张子厚先生书，后世称为“定性书”）</span><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1059&endYear=1059')\">1059年</a>，任鄠县主簿，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>偶成。戏题。题淮南寺。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">偶成<span class=\"small\">（时作鄠县主簿）</span>（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押先韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->云淡风轻近午天，望<span class=\"small\">①</span>花随柳过前川。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->旁人不识予心乐，将谓偷闲学少年。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 《永乐大典》卷八一六五作傍</span></div></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">戏题（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->曾是去年赏春日，春光过了又逡巡。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->却是去年春自去，我心依旧去年春。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">题淮南寺（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押尤韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->南去北来休便休，白蘋吹尽楚江秋。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->道人不是悲秋客，一任晚山相对愁。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年2月</a>，在鄠县游鄠山，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>游鄠县山十二首。白云道中。马上偶成。游紫阁山。猕猴。高观谷。草堂。长啸岩中得冰以石敲餐甚佳。游重云。长啸洞北回望大顶如列屏障比到山前却不见盖为仙掌所蔽。凌霄三峰。云际山。下山偶成。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">高观谷（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押东韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->轰雷叠鼓响前峰，来自彤云翠蔼中。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->洞壑积阴成气象，鬼神凭暗弄威风。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->喷崖雨露千寻湿，落石珠玑万颗红。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->纵有虬龙难驻足，还应不是旱时功。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">草堂（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押东韵</div><br /><div class=\"titleNote\"><span class=\"label\">题注：</span><span class=\"comment\">寺在竹林之心，其竹盖将十顷</span></div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->参差台殿绿云中，四面筼筜一径通。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->曾读华阳真诰上，神仙居在碧琳宫。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">草堂 长啸岩中得冰以石敲餐甚佳（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押阳韵</div><br /><div class=\"titleNote\"><span class=\"label\">题注：</span><span class=\"comment\">寺在竹林之心，其竹盖将十顷</span></div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->车倦人烦渴思长，岩中冰片玉成方。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->老仙笑我尘劳久，乞与云膏洗俗肠。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">草堂 长啸洞北回望大顶如列屏幛比到山前却不见盖为仙掌所蔽（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押寒韵</div><br /><div class=\"titleNote\"><span class=\"label\">题注：</span><span class=\"comment\">寺在竹林之心，其竹盖将十顷</span></div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->行尽重云几曲山，回头方见碧峰寒。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->天将仙掌都遮断，元恐尘中俗眼看。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年2月</a>，在鄠县，游鄠山归。<span class='label'>作品：</span>是游也得小松黄杨各四本植于公署之西窗戏作五绝呈邑令张寺丞。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">是游也得小松黄杨各四本植于公署之西窗戏作五绝呈邑令张寺丞<span class=\"small\">（兴宗）</span>（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押庚韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->中春时节百花明，何必繁弦列管声。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->借问近郊行乐地，潢溪山水照人清。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><br /><div class=\"title\">　　 其二（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押庚韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->心闲不为管弦乐，道胜岂因名利荣。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->莫谓冗官难自适，暇时还得肆游行。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><br /><div class=\"title\">　　 其三（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押先韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->功名不<span class=\"small\">①</span>是关心事，富贵由来自有天。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->任是榷酤亏课利，不过抽得俸中钱。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 涂本作未</span></div><br /><div class=\"title\">　　 其四（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押先韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->有生得遇唐虞圣，为政仍逢守令贤。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->纵得无能闲主簿，嬉游不负艳阳天。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><br /><div class=\"title\">　　 其五（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->狱讼已闻冤滞雪，田农还喜土膏匀。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->只应野叟犹相笑，不与溪山作主人。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1060&endYear=1060')\">1060年</a>，，任鄠县主簿，与万年簿朱公掞、武功簿张山甫号为“关中三杰”<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":36.631222,"Longitude":114.545808,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN1304","Title":"邯郸","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"2cf7dd5d0efc4f4b902076ae85dde562\");'><span id='2cf7dd5d0efc4f4b902076ae85dde562_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年</a>，32岁</div><div id='2cf7dd5d0efc4f4b902076ae85dde562' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1064&endYear=1064')\">1064年</a>，至磁州探望父亲程珦。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.496081,"Longitude":112.857706,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN1405","Title":"晋城","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"97d4be18aa4f4a6abfd5298681cdf814\");'><span id='97d4be18aa4f4a6abfd5298681cdf814_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1066')\">1065-1066年</a>，33-34岁</div><div id='97d4be18aa4f4a6abfd5298681cdf814' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1065&endYear=1065')\">1065年</a>，任晋城县令。<span class='label'>作品：</span>晋城县令题名记。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1066&endYear=1066')\">1066年</a>，任晋城县令，曾到晋祠览胜。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":30.983374,"Longitude":104.288913,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN510681","Title":"广汉","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"e8f4dd2017084077ae73d6d663747686\");'><span id='e8f4dd2017084077ae73d6d663747686_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1067&endYear=1067')\">1067年</a>，35岁</div><div id='e8f4dd2017084077ae73d6d663747686' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1067&endYear=1067')\">1067年</a>，晋城县令秩满改著作佐郎，上任之前与程颐至汉州侍父。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":35.767586,"Longitude":115.035917,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4109","Title":"濮阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"d8a8ce34237e449b9ec26f01fda8aeda\");'><span id='d8a8ce34237e449b9ec26f01fda8aeda_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1071')\">1070-1071年</a>，38-39岁</div><div id='d8a8ce34237e449b9ec26f01fda8aeda' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年4月23日</a>，改镇宁军签判。<span class='label'>作品：</span>谢澶州签判表。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1070&endYear=1070')\">1070年11月26日</a>，任镇宁签判。彭思永卒于金陵。<span class='label'>作品：</span>祭彭侍郎文。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年</a>，任镇宁签判。镇宁河决，全力治河。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年9月26日</a>，任镇宁签判。幼女澶娘出生。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1071&endYear=1071')\">1071年</a>，任镇宁签判。作彭思永行状。<span class='label'>作品：</span>故户部侍郎致仕彭公行状。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.624376,"Longitude":112.460033,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4103","Title":"洛阳","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"5129623ae71042e49ff587f8a36e5bb9\");'><span id='5129623ae71042e49ff587f8a36e5bb9_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1077')\">1072-1077年</a>，40-45岁</div><div id='5129623ae71042e49ff587f8a36e5bb9' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年12月</a>，求监局养亲，罢归居洛。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1072&endYear=1072')\">1072年</a>，与弟程颐讲学于洛，化行乡党，士大夫从学者日夕盈门，虚往实归，人得所欲。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1073&endYear=1073')\">1073年</a>，与程颐讲学于洛。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，居洛。监洛河竹木务。<span class='label'>作品：</span>李寺丞墓志铭。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，居洛。陈襄向宋神宗推荐程颢，称其“性行端醇，明于义理，可备风宪”，终不用。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，程颢、程颐陪侍程珦拜访邵雍于洛阳天津桥，携酒游月陂上。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">游月陂（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押灰韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->月陂堤上四徘徊，北有中天百尺台。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->万物已随秋气改，一樽聊为晚凉开。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->水心云影闲相照，林下泉声静自来。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->世事无端何足计，但逢佳日约重陪。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1074&endYear=1074')\">1074年</a>，居洛。与邵雍诗歌唱和。<span class='label'>作品：</span>和尧夫打乖吟二首。和尧夫首尾吟。和尧夫西街之什二首。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">和邵尧夫打乖吟二首（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->打乖非是要安身，道大方能混世尘。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->陋巷一生颜氏乐，清风千古伯夷贫。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->客求墨妙多携卷，天为诗豪剩借春。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->尽把笑谈亲俗子，德容犹足慰乡人。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><br /><div class=\"title\">　　 其二（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->圣贤事业本经纶，肯为巢由继后尘。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->三币未回伊尹志，万钟难换子舆贫。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->且因经世藏千古，已占西轩度十春。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->时止时行皆有命，先生不是打乖人。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">和尧夫首尾吟（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押支韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->先生非是爱吟诗，为要形容至乐时。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->醉里乾坤都寓物，闲来风月更输谁。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->死生有命人何与，消长随时我不悲。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->直到希夷无事处，先生非是爱吟诗。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">和尧夫西街之什二首（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押灰韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->先生相与赏西街，小子亲携<span class=\"small\">①</span>几杖来。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->行次每容参剧<span class=\"small\">②</span>论，坐隅还许侍馀杯。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->槛前流水心同乐，林外青山眼重开。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->时泰身闲难两得，直须乘兴数追陪。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 万历本作持　② 万历本作极</span></div><br /><div class=\"title\">　　 其二（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押灰韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->先生高蹈隐西街，风月犹牵赋咏才。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->暂到邻家赏池馆，便将佳句写琼瑰。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->壮图已让心先快，剧韵仍降字占挼。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->只有一条誇大甚，水边曾未两三杯。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年3月</a>，居洛。诏修三经义，不果。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年10月</a>，居洛。彗见翼轸间，应诏上书，还朝，差知扶沟县，辞，复求监当官。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1075&endYear=1075')\">1075年10月</a>，居洛。叔父程璠卒于河南。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1076&endYear=1076')\">1076年</a>，居洛。吴充举荐程颢，无果。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年春</a>，居洛。吕公著起知河阳，程颢同贾昌衡、司马光饯于福先寺上东院。<span class='label'>作品：</span>送吕晦叔赴河阳。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">送吕晦叔赴河阳（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押庚韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->晓日都门飐旆旌，晚风铙吹入三城。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->知公再为苍生起，不是寻常刺史行。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，居洛，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>和花庵。和诸公梅台。后一日再和。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">和花庵（宋·程颢）<br />　　五言律诗　押歌韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->得意即为适，种花非贵多。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->一区才丈席，满目自云萝。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->静听禽声乐，闲招月色过。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->期公在康济，终奈此情何。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">和诸公梅台（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押庚韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->急须乘兴赏春英，莫待空枝谩寄声。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->淑景暖风前日事，淡云微雨此时情。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">后一日再和（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->常劝嬉游须及辰，莫辞巾屦染埃尘。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->秪应风雨梅台上，已减前时一半春。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，居洛，有文。<span class='label'>作品：</span>颜乐亭铭。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"4f2c9ae4d7d743c09f5196dc58ef5978\");'><span id='4f2c9ae4d7d743c09f5196dc58ef5978_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年</a>，45岁</div><div id='4f2c9ae4d7d743c09f5196dc58ef5978' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年8月19日</a>，回洛阳葬亲。程珦葬其弟程璠、程瑜于河南伊川先茔，令程颢作墓志铭。<span class='label'>作品：</span>程郎中墓志铭。程殿丞墓志铭。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1077&endYear=1077')\">1077年8月19日</a>，回洛阳葬亲。幼女澶娘夭折。<span class='label'>作品：</span>澶娘墓志铭。<br /></div><div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"76ba491407e246f7a677ff9592eb115d\");'><span id='76ba491407e246f7a677ff9592eb115d_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1083')\">1082-1083年</a>，50-51岁</div><div id='76ba491407e246f7a677ff9592eb115d' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年</a>，居颍昌。杨时有书信，请教春秋之学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1082&endYear=1082')\">1082年冬</a>，居洛，刘绚拜访程颢。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年8月</a>，刘绚拜见程颢于洛阳。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.065909,"Longitude":114.401329,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN411621","Title":"扶沟","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"9689f04159354585bd2840e656aa1f24\");'><span id='9689f04159354585bd2840e656aa1f24_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1080')\">1078-1080年</a>，46-48岁</div><div id='9689f04159354585bd2840e656aa1f24' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，扶沟知县任上，奉命至陕祷雨。<span class='label'>作品：</span>陪陆子履游白石万固。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">陪陆子履游白石万固（宋·程颢）<br />　　押阳韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->条山苍苍河流黄，中蒲形势天下彊。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->帝得贤侯殿一方，四年不更慰民望。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->元丰戊午季春月，上心闵雨愁黎苍。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->使车四出走群望，我亦奉命来侯<span class=\"small\">①</span>疆。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->情诚感格天意顺，诏书才下雨已霶。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->病麦还青禾出土，野农鼓舞歌君王。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->故人相见不道旧，为雨欢喜殊未央。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->圣主宽忧小臣乐，自可放荡舒胸肠。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->白石万固皆胜地，主人为我携壶觞。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->况逢佳日俗所尚，车马未晓填康庄。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->扶提十里杂老幼，迤逦千骑明戈枪。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->初听鸣铙入青霭，渐见朱旆辉朝阳。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->遨头自是谢康乐，后乘独惭元漫郎。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->侯来虽知有宾客，众喜更为将丰穰。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->临溪坐石遍岩谷，幽处往往闻丝簧。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->山光似迎好客动，日景定为游人长。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->乘高望远兴不尽，恋恋不知歧路忙。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->人生汨没苦百态，得此乐事真难常。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->我辞佳境已惆怅，侯亦那得久此乡。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->他时会合重相语，辜负泉石何能忘。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 弘治本、万历本、涂本作陕</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，扶沟知县任上，与孔宗翰有诗歌往来。<span class='label'>作品：</span>下白径岭先寄孔周翰郎中。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">下白径岭先寄孔周翰郎中（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押豪韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->骤经微雨过芳郊，转觉长河气象豪。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->归骑已登吴坂峻，飞云犹认华山高。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->门前岐路通西国，城上楼台压巨涛。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->欲问甘棠旧风化，主人邀客醉香醪。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，任扶沟知县，谢良佐受学于扶沟。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1078&endYear=1078')\">1078年</a>，任扶沟知县。程颐侍行，二程以倡明道学为己任，设庠序，聚邑人子弟教之。游酢来从学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年2月</a>，任扶沟知县。诏判武学，以李定、何正臣论罢，仍复扶沟县任。<span class='label'>作品：</span>陈公廙园修禊事席上赋。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">陈公廙园修禊事席上赋（宋·程颢）<br />　　五言律诗　押侵韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->盛集兰亭旧，风流洛社今。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->坐中无俗客，水曲有清音。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->香篆来还去，花枝泛复沉。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->未须愁日暮，天际是轻阴。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年2月</a>，在扶沟县任，郊游赋诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>郊行即事。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">郊行即事（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言律诗　押微韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->芳原绿野恣行时，春入遥山碧四围。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->兴逐乱红穿柳巷，困临流<span class=\"small\">①</span>水坐苔矶。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->莫辞盏酒十分醉，秪恐风花一片飞。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->况是清明好天气，不妨游衍莫忘归。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 弘治本、万历本作溪</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1079&endYear=1079')\">1079年6月</a>，在扶沟县任，舅父侯可卒。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年2月</a>，任扶沟知县。为舅父侯可作墓志铭。<span class='label'>作品：</span>华阴侯先生墓志铭。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":34.041737,"Longitude":113.858804,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN411","Title":"许昌","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"24245c91276142bda080b6d5e5355047\");'><span id='24245c91276142bda080b6d5e5355047_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1081')\">1080-1081年</a>，48-49岁</div><div id='24245c91276142bda080b6d5e5355047' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1080&endYear=1080')\">1080年6月</a>，罢扶沟任，居颍昌。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，居颍昌，知府韩维从游问学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，居颍昌，暇日同知府韩维游西湖，有诗。<span class='label'>作品：</span>酬韩持国资政湖上独酌见赠。<div class=\"poem\">\r\n<div class=\"title\">酬韩持国资政湖上独酌见赠（宋·程颢）<br />　　七言绝句　押真韵</div><div class=\"content\"><p><!--S-->对花酌酒公能乐，饭糗羹藜我自贫。<!--E--></p><p><!--S-->若语至诚无内外，却应分别更迷真<span class=\"small\">①</span>。<!--E--></p></div><!--CE--><div class=\"footer\"><span class=\"label\">按：</span><span class=\"comment\">① 自注：韩诗云：曲肱饮水程夫子，宴坐焚香范使君。愧我未能忘外乐，缘尊红芰对西曛。</span></div></div>\r\n<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1081&endYear=1081')\">1081年</a>，杨时拜师于颍昌，深得程颢嘉赏，及归，送之出门，谓坐客曰“吾道南矣”。<br /></div>"},{"Latitude":33.772051,"Longitude":113.198935,"OffsetLeft":0,"OffsetTop":0,"Invisible":false,"RegionId":"CN4104","Title":"平顶山","Detail":"<div class='label1'><a href='javascript: DetailSwitch(\"72b20dfda2554510bbd91e9dac7d45aa\");'><span id='72b20dfda2554510bbd91e9dac7d45aa_link' class='switch'>—</span></a><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1085')\">1083-1085年</a>，51-53岁</div><div id='72b20dfda2554510bbd91e9dac7d45aa' class='detail'><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，监汝州酒税。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，朱公掞拜见先生于汝，归谓人曰：“光庭在春风中坐了一个月。”<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年11月</a>，居汝。富弼卒。<span class='label'>作品：</span>祭富韩公文。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1083&endYear=1083')\">1083年</a>，居汝。杨时有书信，请教春秋之学。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1084&endYear=1084')\">1084年</a>，夫人彭氏卒于汝州。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年3月</a>，居汝。宋哲宗即位，改承议郎。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年3月</a>，居汝。宋哲宗即位后，宋朝继任宰相司马光、吕公著的要务，在程颢看来，是与元丰大臣齐心协力共谋大政，而非分党。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年5月</a>，居汝。召为宗正寺丞，未行而疾终。<br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewDetail('scope=&author=&beginYear=1085&endYear=1085')\">1085年6月15日</a>，以疾终于汝州。<br /></div>"}],"Title":"程颢 <span class='inlineComment2'>(1032-1085)</span>","Detail":"<p class='inlineComment2'>引用书目：池生春《明道先生年谱》　录入整理：王建生</p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(0, 4, 116.9908965, 28.736276, 8)\">0-21岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(0)\">黄陂</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(1)\">丹阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(2)\">大余</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(3)\">南京</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(4, 12, 111.545902, 33.807298, 7)\">23-38岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(4)\">凤县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(5)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(6)\">户县</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(7)\">南京</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(8)\">邯郸</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(9)\">晋城</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(10)\">广汉</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(11)\">开封</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(12, 16, 113.747975, 35.195981, 9)\">38-45岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(12)\">濮阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(13)\">洛阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(14)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(15)\">洛阳</a></p><p><a href=\"javascript: ViewRoute(16, 21, 113.430681, 34.287496, 10)\">45-53岁</a><br /><a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(16)\">开封</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(17)\">扶沟</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(18)\">许昌</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(19)\">洛阳</a> → <a href=\"javascript: ViewPoint(20)\">平顶山</a></p>"}]}